{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)"},"section_detail":{"1":{"hadithnumber_first":1,"hadithnumber_last":390,"arabicnumber_first":1,"arabicnumber_last":390}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":78,"arabicnumber":78,"text":"Rapporté par Aishah (la mère des croyants) رضي الله عنها : Mes mains et celles du Messager d’Allah ﷺ allaient tour à tour dans le même récipient pendant que nous faisions nos ablutions","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Hasan Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Hasan"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Isnaad Hasan"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":78}}]}